monobook is 'skins/monobook/headbg.jpg'. Replace that with another JPG
and the background Just Works(TM). Use this configuration in
'/var/www/mediawiki116/LocalSettings.php' to make the default logo
disappear:

<pre>
// Setting to blank to show background with logo on it. It remains clickable,
